abstract: >-
  GEO-Master is an open, case-driven handbook and dataset project for studying
  how brands are discovered, mentioned, cited, recommended, and accurately
  described by generative search and AI answer engines. It includes evidence
  standards, operational playbooks, reusable templates, third-party case
  teardowns, and reproducible experiment designs.